{
  "stem": "10564.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she [INAUDIBLE] she didn't care because she couldn't take care of this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she said, all right, you eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What we eat, you eat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm looking at a picture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His son is SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "SS is-- they swore their legion to Hitler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They never surrender.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They obey, obey command without question.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anything.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If they tell him, kill the mother, probably they would do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now so we supposed to go ahead and milk the cow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got a bucket of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My friend, young boy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After we make the bucket, we put the bucket on the side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He put his nose in it, and drinked the milk right from the bucket.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A few days later he died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He got loose stomach.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing to stop that because we never got used to it, to the fat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We never eat fat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Only dry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we found out this is danger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was an older guy from us, a little more older than us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Understand a little bit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, let's make it potato.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A little bit milk. 90% potatoes and a little milk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Slowly, slowly, slowly, slowly the stomach should get used to it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we took bread and sometimes shared a ham.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Sometimes they were hanging that to dry out from a pig.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A whole leg, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So now we like to eat this because they would give us this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So slowly, slowly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But he couldn't survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Whatever we done to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He wouldn't survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were four of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were there together in January, February, March.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "April a Wehrmacht commander, maybe about 50 of them, with trucks, with cars, with machine guns, with guns came in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
